                    <p class="text-white">
                        I’m a junior web developer and digital enthusiast, passionate about building smart, efficient, and impactful solutions. 
                        I work with some popular technologies, and also explore database and UI/UX design
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-white-50">
                        I’m currently involved in developing digital tools for businesses, especially in logistics and social impact sectors. 
